column2: SELECT TOP #  wiseXsdss.sdss_objid, wiseXsdss.wise_cntr, match_dist,  sdss_best.ra, sdss_best.dec, sdss_best.specObjID,   sdss_best.class FROM   WISE_xmatch wiseXsdss  JOIN   WISE_allsky allwise ON wiseXsdss.wise_cntr = allwise.cntr  JOIN   SpecObj sdss_best on wiseXsdss.sdss_objid = sdss_best.bestObjID WHERE  sdss_best.class = &&&  AND sdss_best.zWarning = #
